│  12 // was found, the SLP vectorizer performs  │
│ vectorization on the tree.                     │
│  13 //                                         │
│  14 // The pass is inspired by the work        │
│ described in the paper:                        │
│  15 //  "Loop-Aware SLP in GCC" by Ira Rosen,  │
